Eddie Phillips (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eddie_Phillips_(actor) 0 Eddie Phillips (August 14, 1899 – February 22, 1965) was an American actor. He appeared in 180 films between 1913 and 1952. He was born in Philadelphia, Pennsylvania and died in Hollywood, California.
